    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. It has been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really wonderful shape! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the maintenance, so it\u2019s running smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure. It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is just waiting for the right person to take the wheel. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that's been well-loved, this is the one! Feel free to shoot me a message\u2014I'd love to chat and answer any questions you have!",
