    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-gated Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and a bespoke suspension setup, this unit offers exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. Recent major service included a VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the dual-overhead-cam valvetrain operates within factory tolerances. A driver-focused example ready for spirited canyon carving or track-day duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
