    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive shape for its age. The exterior boasts a deep luster with only minor road-wear blemishes that do not detract from its overall curb appeal. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and well-preserved; the upholstery is firm, and all dashboard controls function as intended. Mechanically, it is sound, having received consistent fluid changes and preventative maintenance. It provides a smooth, reliable ride with plenty of life left for its next owner. A perfect balance of value and quality for someone looking for a dependable, attractive car without the new-car price tag.",
