    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and I honestly think you\u2019re going to love it. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in great shape, running smoothly and ready for many more adventures. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s clean and ready to go today. If you\u2019re looking for a solid vehicle that won\u2019t let you down, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
