      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain remains crisp, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis effectively manages the torque bias of the M-variable differential lock. Riding on a refreshed suspension with upgraded bushings, this example offers sharp turn-in and exceptional lateral stability. While it shows honest driver-grade patina, the mechanical fundamentals are robust, making it a purist's choice for spirited driving.",
